msgid "0:梨深は――梨深って呼んでいいのかどうか分からないけど――ホントに完璧に記憶を失っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "0:Rimi had—if I could call her Rimi—totally lost her memories.[%p]"

msgid "100:あるいは、この梨深は元々記憶なんて持っていない、とも言えるかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "100:Or maybe this Rimi never had any memories in the first place.[%p]"

msgid "200:[name]梨深[line]「あたしは、りみっていうの？」[%p]"
msgstr "200:[name]梨深[line]My name's Rimi?[%p]"

msgid "300:[name]拓巳[line]「うん、そ、そうだよ……。咲畑梨深」[%p]"
msgstr "300:[name]拓巳[line]Y-Yeah. That's right. Rimi Sakihata.[%p]"

msgid "400:[name]梨深[line]「さきはたりみ」[%p]"
msgstr "400:[name]梨深[line]Rimi Sakihata.[%p]"

msgid "500:[name]梨深[line]「そうなんだ〜」[%p]"
msgstr "500:[name]梨深[line]Ooh, I see.[%p]"

msgid "600:その口振りは、まるで他人事だ。[%p]"
msgstr "600:She spoke like the name meant nothing to her at all.[%p]"

msgid "700:[name]梨深[line]「あなたは？」[%p]"
msgstr "700:[name]梨深[line]Who are you?[%p]"

msgid "800:[name]梨深[line]「おなまえ、なんていうのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "800:[name]梨深[line]What's your name?[%p]"

msgid "900:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕は、西條拓巳……」[%p]"
msgstr "900:[name]拓巳[line]I-I'm Takumi Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "1000:こんな基本的なことを一から教えなくちゃいけないなんて……。[linebreak]この先のことを考えると、暗澹とした気分になる。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:She didn't even know my name? I felt a little depressed, thinking about all the other things I'd have to tell her.[%p]"

msgid "1100:[name]梨深[line]「にしじょうたくみ」[%p]"
msgstr "1100:[name]梨深[line]Takumi Nishijo...[%p]"

msgid "1200:[name]梨深[line]「タク、だね！」[%p]"
msgstr "1200:[name]梨深[line]I'll call you Taku, then![%p]"

msgid "1300:[name]拓巳[line]「え……」[%p]"
msgstr "1300:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "1400:[name]梨深[line]「タク！」[%p]"
msgstr "1400:[name]梨深[line]Taku![%p]"

msgid "1500:同じだ……。その呼び方は、同じなんだね……。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:The same... She was calling me the same thing.[%p]"

msgid "1600:[name]梨深[line]「ねえねえ、タク〜。あのね、あたしね、手が、べとべとしてるの」[%p]"
msgstr "1600:[name]梨深[line]Hey, hey, Taku! My hands are all sticky.[%p]"

msgid "1700:手には、乾いた血がべっとりとこびりついている。[linebreak]赤黒く変色したそれは、こずぴぃの血だ――そのはずだ。[linebreak]こずぴぃの死体は消えていたけど、血だけは残っている。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:There was dried blood stuck to her hands. It was dark black, and belonged to Kozupii. At least, it probably did. Kozupii had disappeared, but the blood was still there.[%p]"

msgid "1800:[name]梨深[line]「べとべと、やだなぁ」[%p]"
msgstr "1800:[name]梨深[line]I don't like having sticky hands.[%p]"

msgid "1900:自分の手を見て、梨深はしょんぼりしている。[linebreak]こずぴぃの笑顔を思い出し、僕はうずくような胸の痛みを覚えた。[linebreak]それをこらえつつ、濡れタオルを用意した。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:She was looking at her hands glumly. I remembered Kozupii's smile and felt an aching pain in my chest. I tried to ignore it as I went to get a wet towel.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]拓巳[line]「ほ、ほら、手、出して……」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]拓巳[line]C-Come on, hold out your hands.[%p]"

msgid "2100:僕の言葉に、梨深はおずおずと両手を差し出してきた。[linebreak]タオルで、その血を拭っていく。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:Rimi nervously offered me both her hands. I wiped them with a towel.[%p]"

msgid "2200:白かったタオルは、みるみる赤く染まる。[linebreak]キレイに拭い取るには、少し強めに擦らなければならなかった。[linebreak]指と指の間まで、ゴシゴシと擦っていると――[%p]"
msgstr "2200:The white towel quickly turned red. I had to scrub pretty hard to get it all off. When I started scrubbing the spots between her fingers...[%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]梨深[line]「あはは。くすぐったい」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]梨深[line]Ahahah! It tickles.[%p]"

msgid "2400:梨深が楽しそうに笑う。[linebreak]なんで自分の手に血がこびりついているのか、その理由についてはまったく気にならないらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:She laughed happily. She didn't seem to wonder in the slightest why she had blood on her hands.[%p]"

msgid "2500:くそぅ、呑気なもんだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:Damn it... Why was I the only one who was concerned here?[%p]"

msgid "2600:っていうか、手ぐらい自分で拭けよ。[linebreak]どうして僕がこんな子供の世話みたいなこと、[linebreak]しなくちゃいけないんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:And why couldn't she wipe her own hands? Why did I have to take care of this little girl?[%p]"

msgid "2700:……なんて、そんなこと言えるはずはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:No. I couldn't think that way.[%p]"

msgid "2800:梨深は、僕を守ろうとしてくれたんだ。[linebreak]そのせいで、故意なのか事故なのか分からないけど、人を殺して。[linebreak]そして、心が壊れてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:Rimi had tried to protect me. And, whether intentionally or not, she'd killed someone in the process. And that had broken her.[%p]"

msgid "2900:だから、僕には、今の梨深を放り出すことなんてできない。[linebreak]梨深がこうなったのは、僕のせいでもあるんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:That's why I couldn't abandon her. It was partially my fault that she'd ended up this way.[%p]"

msgid "3000:[name]拓巳[line]「ほ、ほら、キレイに、なったよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "3000:[name]拓巳[line]L-Look, you're all clean now.[%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]梨深[line]「ありがとー」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]梨深[line]Thanks![%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]梨深[line]「ぴかぴかだぁ、あたしの手」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]梨深[line]My hands are all clean![%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]梨深[line]「すっきりしたよっ」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]梨深[line]I feel so much better.[%p]"

msgid "3400:僕の手を握って、指を絡めて。[linebreak]無邪気に、ブンブンと上下に振る。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:She grabbed my hand and wrapped her fingers around mine. She was shaking our hands up and down, innocently.[%p]"

msgid "3500:とても楽しそうで、まるで子供みたいで。[linebreak]その笑顔を見て、僕はなぜか、とても切なくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:She looked like a child, having the time of her life. For some reason, seeing her smile made me feel sad.[%p]"

msgid "3600:[name]拓巳[line]「ねえ、梨深……。君は、ぼ、僕を、守ってくれる？」[%p]"
msgstr "3600:[name]拓巳[line]Hey... Rimi... W-Will you protect me?[%p]"

msgid "3700:[name]梨深[line]「まもる？\u3000なにを？」[%p]"
msgstr "3700:[name]梨深[line]Protect? What?[%p]"

msgid "3800:[name]拓巳[line]「僕を……」[%p]"
msgstr "3800:[name]拓巳[line]Me...[%p]"

msgid "3900:[name]梨深[line]「あのね、あたしね、よくわかんない」[%p]"
msgstr "3900:[name]梨深[line]Um, I really don't understand.[%p]"

msgid "4000:[name]梨深[line]「でもね、タクはあたしのおともだちだから、あたしにしんせつにしてくれるよね」[%p]"
msgstr "4000:[name]梨深[line]But you're my friend, and you'll be nice to me, right?[%p]"

msgid "4100:[name]梨深[line]「だからね、あたし、タクがいてくれてよかったよ。えへへ」[%p]"
msgstr "4100:[name]梨深[line]So, I'm glad you're here! Hehehe.[%p]"

msgid "4200:ダメだ。梨深は、もうダメだ。[linebreak]僕を守ってくれる梨深は、もういないんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:This was no good. There was no use counting on Rimi anymore. The Rimi who was going to protect me was nowhere to be seen.[%p]"

msgid "4300:僕はうなだれた。[linebreak]梨深はここにいるべきじゃない。[linebreak]梨深の家って、どこにあるんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:I sighed and my head slumped forward. Rimi didn't belong here. Where was her home?[%p]"

msgid "4400:梨深の家族に連絡すべきかと思ったけど、彼女の持ち物からは連絡先を特定するものがなにも見つからなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:I thought about calling her parents, but I couldn't find anything with their contact information on it in her things.[%p]"

msgid "4500:学校に行けば、教師が住所を知ってるんだろうけど、今日はもう遅いから入れないだろうし。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:The teachers at school would probably know, but it was too late in the day for that.[%p]"

msgid "4600:そもそもよく考えてみれば、僕は梨深についてあまりになにも知らない。どこに住んでいるのか。家族は何人なのか。誕生日は？\u3000血液型は？[%p]"
msgstr "4600:I realized that I didn't really know that much about Rimi. Where did she live? What was her family like? What was her birthday or her blood type?[%p]"

msgid "4700:僕は、なにも知らない……。[linebreak]とにかく、僕じゃもうどうすることもできない……。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:I didn't know anything about her. There was nothing I could do.[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]梨深[line]「タクー、タクー」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]梨深[line]Taku! Taku![%p]"

msgid "4900:梨深が僕の服の袖を引っ張り、名前を呼んでくる。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:Rimi was tugging at the hem of my clothing and calling my name.[%p]"

msgid "5000:[name]梨深[line]「ねえねえ、タクー」[%p]"
msgstr "5000:[name]梨深[line]Hey, hey, Taku![%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]梨深[line]「あたしね、おなかぺこぺこー」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]梨深[line]I'm really hungry![%p]"

msgid "5200:今は、何時だろう。[linebreak]外はもう日が暮れている。夕食時だ。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:What time was it? It was already dark outside. Time for dinner.[%p]"

msgid "5300:でもあいにく、ここには買い置きなんてない。[linebreak]なにか、買ってこないと。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:But unfortunately, I didn't have anything in the house. I needed to go buy something.[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なにが、食べたい？」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]拓巳[line]W-What do you want to eat?[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]梨深[line]「ん？\u3000んー？」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]梨深[line]Hm? Hmm?[%p]"

msgid "5600:記憶喪失の場合、食べ物のことも忘れちゃったりするのかな？[linebreak]どんなメニューがこの世の中には存在するのか知らないとか、味も分からなくなってるとか。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:When you had amnesia, did you forget about food, too? Maybe you didn't know what kind of foods there were, or what they tasted like?[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]梨深[line]「あ、そうだ！\u3000あのね、あたし、おそばがたべたい！」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]梨深[line]Oh, I know! Um, I want soba noodles![%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]拓巳[line]「おそば……？」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]拓巳[line]Soba noodles?[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]梨深[line]「おそば、すき！」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]梨深[line]I like soba noodles![%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]拓巳[line]「す、好き、なの……？」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]拓巳[line]You do?[%p]"

msgid "6100:[name]梨深[line]「すき！」[%p]"
msgstr "6100:[name]梨深[line]I do![%p]"

msgid "6200:[name]拓巳[line]「なんで？\u3000た、食べたこと、あるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "6200:[name]拓巳[line]Why? H-Have you ever eaten them before?[%p]"

msgid "6300:[name]梨深[line]「たべたこと？\u3000んー、ないかも……」[%p]"
msgstr "6300:[name]梨深[line]Eaten them? Hmm... maybe not.[%p]"

msgid "6400:[name]梨深[line]「でもね、おそばは、すきだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]梨深[line]But I like soba noodles![%p]"

msgid "6500:どういうことだ？[linebreak]記憶が戻り始めてる？[linebreak]あるいは前の梨深の食べ物の好みだけを、覚えてる？[%p]"
msgstr "6500:What was going on? Were her memories coming back? Or did she keep the memories of the old Rimi's favorite foods, and lose everything else?[%p]"

msgid "6600:記憶が戻ってくれるなら、僕としても助かるんだけど……。[linebreak]とりあえずスーパーにそばを買いに行こう。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:It'd be a big help to me if her memories came back, but... I decided I may as well go to the supermarket to get some soba noodles.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]拓巳[line]「梨深、こ、ここで待ってて。ぜ、絶対、外に出ちゃダメだ」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]拓巳[line]Rimi, s-stay here. D-Don't go outside for any reason![%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]梨深[line]「はーい」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]梨深[line]Okay![%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]拓巳[line]「……ビシィ」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]拓巳[line]Snap![%p]"

msgid "7000:試しに、僕は前の梨深がよくしていたポーズをやってみた。[linebreak]片手を、敬礼するように頭に添える。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:I tried mimicking the pose that Rimi always used to do. I put one hand up to my head like a salute.[%p]"

msgid "7100:これで、梨深がなにかを思い出してくれるなら……。[linebreak]そう思ったんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:Maybe this would help her remember something, I thought. But...[%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]梨深[line]「びし？\u3000なぁに？\u3000かっこいいね！」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]梨深[line]Snap? What? That's really cool![%p]"

msgid "7300:全然通じなかった。[linebreak]むしろ興味津々という感じで目を輝かせている。[linebreak]すごく恥ずかしくなって、僕は逃げるように部屋を出た。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:It didn't work at all. She was looking at me with eyes filled with wonder and excitement. I suddenly became extremely embarrassed, and ran out of the room.[%p]"

msgid "7400:スーパーへの道すがら、近くに警察がいないかを確認してみる。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:On my way to the supermarket, I looked around to see if any cops were nearby.[%p]"

msgid "7500:セナとこずぴぃの死体は、やっぱり消えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:Sena and Kozupii's bodies had both disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "7600:もしも警察が近くにいるなら、目撃者がいた可能性がある。[linebreak]いないなら……誰にも見つかっていないっていうこと。[linebreak]もしそうなら、しばらくはバレないかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:If the police were nearby, that would mean there was a witness. And if they weren't... that would mean nobody had seen what happened. If it was the latter, that might mean nobody was going to find out for a while.[%p]"

msgid "7700:もちろん警察だけじゃなく、『将軍』がどこかから現れないかと、常に物陰などを警戒した。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:Of course, I also watched the shadows constantly to see if Shogun was lurking nearby, too.[%p]"

msgid "7800:幸いにも、例の“神の視線”は、今のところ気配を感じない。[linebreak]それでも、夜は外に出たくなかった。[linebreak]闇が怖い。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:Fortunately, I wasn't feeling the Gaze of God. But still, I didn't want to go out at night. The dark scared me.[%p]"

msgid "7900:そしてその闇の奥に、ぼうっと、こずぴぃやセナが死んだときの光景が浮かび上がってくる。２人の無残に変わり果てた姿が、浮かび上がってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:And when I looked into the dark, I could see Sena and Kozupii dying in front of me again. I could see their mangled corpses.[%p]"

msgid "8000:僕はすぐに目をそらし、自分の足許だけを見つめて、スーパーへ急いだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:I quickly looked away and stared down at my feet as I hurried to the supermarket.[%p]"

msgid "8100:ベースに戻り、カセットコンロを引っ張り出してきて、外でそばを茹でる。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:When I got back to the Base, I pulled out the portable gas burner to boil some soba noodles outside.[%p]"

msgid "8200:コンテナハウスの中だと、換気ができないし燃えやすそうなものがたくさん散らかってるしで、危ないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:There was no air circulation inside the container house, and there was a lot of stuff that was flammable, too. It was too dangerous to do it inside.[%p]"

msgid "8300:鍋に適当にそばを放り込む。[linebreak]もちろんインスタントの乾麺だ。[linebreak]梨深はそれを興味深そうに眺めていた。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:I tossed some soba into the pot. Of course, they were cheap, dry, instant noodles. Rimi was looking at the pot, fascinated.[%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]梨深[line]「おそばって、こうやってつくるんだねー」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]梨深[line]So, this is how you make soba, huh?[%p]"

msgid "8500:こずぴぃの血溜まりは、まだそこにある。[linebreak]もうほとんど乾いていて、夜ということもあって表面的には黒い染みにしか見えない。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:The pool of blood from when Kozupii had died was still there. It was almost dry now, and at night, it just looked like a dark stain.[%p]"

msgid "8600:その上に、部屋にたまっていた空きダンボールを、たたんで敷く。[linebreak]こんなことしたって、なんの解決にもならないけど、なるべく目に入れたくなかったんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:I broke down some of the cardboard boxes from my room and put them over it. It didn't actually help anything, but at least it saved me from having to look at it.[%p]"

msgid "8700:[name]梨深[line]「タクー、タクー！\u3000こぼれそうだよー！」[%p]"
msgstr "8700:[name]梨深[line]Taku! Taku! It's going to boil over![%p]"

msgid "8800:梨深に呼ばれてコンロのところに戻った。[%p]"
msgstr "8800:I went back to the burner when Rimi called my name.[%p]"

msgid "8900:沸騰しすぎて、麺を入れたお湯が溢れそうになっている。[linebreak]梨深はそれをただ「おおー」と言いながら見ているだけで、動こうとしない。[%p]"
msgstr "8900:It was boiling too much, and at the point of overflowing out of the pot. Rimi was just watching it, letting out small gasps of amazement. She wasn't moving at all otherwise.[%p]"

msgid "9000:[name]拓巳[line]「火を、け、消して」[%p]"
msgstr "9000:[name]拓巳[line]T-Turn off the heat![%p]"

msgid "9100:[name]梨深[line]「ん？\u3000んー？」[%p]"
msgstr "9100:[name]梨深[line]Hm? Hmm?[%p]"

msgid "9200:梨深は首を傾げながらも、コンロのスイッチをひねった。[linebreak]――強くなる方へ。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:Confused, she turned the dial on the burner. And made it hotter.[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]梨深[line]「わー。あふれたよー。すごーい」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]梨深[line]Wow! It boiled over! Amazing![%p]"

msgid "9400:[name]拓巳[line]「いや、す、すごいじゃ、ないでしょ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]拓巳[line]N-No... It's not amazing![%p]"

msgid "9500:慌てて梨深を押しのけて、火を消す。[linebreak]お湯が大量に吹きこぼれてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:I quickly shoved her out of the way and turned off the heat. A lot of the water had spilled out of the pot.[%p]"

msgid "9600:まあいいや……。食べられさえすれば、そばの味とかコシとか、そんなものにそれほど気を回す必要はない。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Well, whatever… As long as it was edible, I didn't need to think too much about how firm the noodles were, or how it tasted.[%p]"

msgid "9700:というわけで鍋から麺を取り出して湯切りし、流しでさっと水洗い。[linebreak]そうしろって、説明書きに書いてあったからで、別に手慣れてるわけじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "9700:I drained the noodles and washed them with cold water. I didn't know much of anything about cooking soba noodles. I just did it because that's what the instructions said.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]拓巳[line]「ひ、冷やしと、あったかいのと、ど、どっちがいい？」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]拓巳[line]D-Do you want them hot... or cold?[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]梨深[line]「つめたいの！」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]梨深[line]Cold![%p]"

msgid "10000:どんぶりに麺を盛り、一緒に買ってきためんつゆをどばどばとかけた。[linebreak]薬味はねぎのみ。適当に刻んで、できあがり。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:I put them in a bowl and poured in some of the broth I'd bought at the store along with the noodles. For toppings, I had green onions. I sliced them up, and we were done.[%p]"

msgid "10100:急いで梨深を連れて部屋の中に入った。[linebreak]後片付けは、明日、明るくなってからやろう。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:I hurried back into the room with Rimi in tow. I could clean up tomorrow, when it was light.[%p]"

msgid "10200:今は、できるだけ外にいたくなかった。[linebreak]まだわずかに血の臭いが漂っていたし。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:For now, I didn't want to be outside unless I absolutely had to. I could still smell the blood.[%p]"

msgid "10300:なんだか、オカルトチックだけど、怖かったんだ。[linebreak]血まみれのセナとこずぴぃが、今にもゾンビみたいに歩いて現れそうな気がして。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:And even though I knew it was silly, I was still scared. It felt like Sena and Kozupii might come staggering out of the darkness covered in blood, like zombies.[%p]"

msgid "10400:[name]梨深[line]「ねえタク。たべていい？\u3000たべていい？」[%p]"
msgstr "10400:[name]梨深[line]Hey, Taku. Can I eat? Can I eat?[%p]"

msgid "10500:梨深には、僕のような深刻な悩みはないらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:Rimi didn't share any of my worries, it seemed.[%p]"

msgid "10600:いや、だからこそ梨深は前の人格から新しい人格に変わったのかもしれない。人を殺したっていう現実をキレイさっぱり忘れるために。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:No, maybe that was why she'd changed from her last personality into this new one, so that she could forget the fact that she'd killed two people.[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]拓巳[line]「ど、どうぞ……」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]拓巳[line]G-Go ahead.[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]梨深[line]「わーい。いただきまーす」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]梨深[line]Yay! Let's eat![%p]"

msgid "10900:梨深は箸を鷲づかみにした。[linebreak]フォークのような使い方だ。[linebreak]丼の縁に口を付けながら、そばをすすっている。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:She grabbed the chopsticks. She was holding them like a fork. She put her lips to the bowl and slurped the noodles up.[%p]"

msgid "11000:――どう見ても[color index="A0FF0000"]ょぅι゛ょ[color index="800000"]の食べ方です。本当にありがとうございました。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:—This was exactly how a [color index="A0FF0000"]el-oh-el-eye[color index="800000"] would eat. Thank you. Thank you very much.[%p]"

msgid "11100:箸の持ち方すら忘れたらしい。[linebreak]そばの作り方も、コンロの火の消し方も、忘れた。[linebreak]その割に、“いただきます”と食事前に言うことは覚えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:She'd forgotten how to use chopsticks too, from the look of it. And how to make soba noodles or turn off a burner, too. But she still knew to say “let's eat” before she ate her food.[%p]"

msgid "11200:物事に対するあらゆる認識が、退行化しているってことか。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:It wasn't amnesia, then. She'd just regressed to a childlike state.[%p]"

msgid "11300:[name]梨深[line]「食べられないよー」[%p]"
msgstr "11300:[name]梨深[line]I can't eat it.[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]拓巳[line]「え？」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]梨深[line]「食べられないー」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]梨深[line]I can't eat it![%p]"

msgid "11600:梨深は、上手に食べられなくてもどかしそうにしていた。[linebreak]そりゃ、あんな食べ方じゃ当たり前だよ。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:Rimi was having trouble eating her noodles, and getting frustrated. She was trying to eat them the wrong way, and it wasn't working.[%p]"

msgid "11700:[name]梨深[line]「食べさせて」[%p]"
msgstr "11700:[name]梨深[line]Feed me.[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]拓巳[line]「なん……だと……？」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]拓巳[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "11900:本気で言ってるの？[linebreak]僕が、梨深に、食べさせるだって？[%p]"
msgstr "11900:Was she serious? Rimi wanted me to feed her?[%p]"

msgid "12000:介護士にでもなった気分だ。[linebreak]それとも父親か？[linebreak]同い年の娘を持つなんて、勘弁してよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I felt like I'd become her nurse. No, maybe her father? Please, I couldn't handle having a daughter my own age![%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]梨深[line]「タクぅ」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]梨深[line]Taku![%p]"

msgid "12200:甘えるようにねだってくるので、僕はため息をつき、仕方なく食べさせてあげることにした。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:She begged me, exactly like a little girl would. I gave in and sighed.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]拓巳[line]「ほ、ほら。あーんして」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]拓巳[line]O-Okay... Open up and say, “Aah.”[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]梨深[line]「あーん」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]梨深[line]Aah![%p]"

msgid "12500:梨深は僕が差し出したそばを口に含み、おいしそうに咀嚼。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:She brought her mouth down on the noodles I offered her and began to chew happily.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]梨深[line]「えへへ。おいしいよ」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]梨深[line]Eheheh. It's yummy.[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、それは、よ、よかった……」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]拓巳[line]G-Good.[%p]"

msgid "12800:ふと、思う。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:Suddenly, I realized.[%p]"

msgid "12900:三次元の女子との、こんな何気ない日常。[linebreak]僕が求めていたのはきっと、こんな毎日なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:This was it. This was normal, everyday life with a 3D girl next to me. This was what I wanted.[%p]"

msgid "13000:エロゲみたいな、劇的なイベントとかは特に起きることもなくて。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:I didn't need any dramatic events, like in an H-game.[%p]"

msgid "13100:ヒロインの抱える心の傷でうだうだしたり、互いに想い合っているのにすれ違ってしまったり、あまつさえ殺人事件に巻き込まれたりすることなく。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:No getting involved in her deep psychological traumas. No minor misunderstandings that blew up into fiascos. No murders to solve.[%p]"

msgid "13200:小説やゲームにしたら、面白くもなんともない、こういう日常を。[linebreak]僕は、求めていた気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:This daily life was far too boring to be in a game or novel. But this is what I wanted.[%p]"

msgid "13300:その日常が、実際に今、こうして目の前にある。[linebreak]しかも僕と一緒にいてくれるのは、梨深だ。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:And now I had it. And it was with Rimi, too.[%p]"

msgid "13400:正直に言う。梨深は、かわいい。[linebreak]僕のことを守ってくれるとも言ってくれた。[linebreak]僕だって、できればずっと、梨深と一緒にいたい。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:To be honest, I thought Rimi was cute. She'd even said she'd protect me. I wanted to be with her forever, if I could.[%p]"

msgid "13500:だけど、こんなのは偽りだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:But this was all a lie.[%p]"

msgid "13600:こんな日常は、決して長くは続かない。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:This life wasn't going to last.[%p]"

msgid "13700:そして、梨深は、梨深じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:And this Rimi wasn't Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "13800:あまりにも儚い時間。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:What I had now could end at any moment.[%p]"

msgid "13900:そう考えると、すごく切なくて。哀しくて。虚しくて。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:And when I thought of that, it made me feel so sad. So lonely, so empty...[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]拓巳[line]「戻ってきてよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]拓巳[line]Come back.[%p]"

msgid "14100:[name]拓巳[line]「梨深、元に、戻ってくれ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14100:[name]拓巳[line]Rimi, come back.[%p]"

msgid "14200:そうつぶやかずにはいられなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I whispered.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]星来[line]「メールだよ〜、ぼけなす♪」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]星来[line]You've got mail, dork![%p]"

msgid "14400:ハッとした。[linebreak]ＰＣからの、星来たんの声。[linebreak]誰かから、メールが来た。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:I gasped. I heard Seira-tan's voice from the computer. Somebody had sent me an email.[%p]"

msgid "14500:『将軍』か……？[%p]"
msgstr "14500:Shogun?[%p]"

msgid "14600:予感がする。[linebreak]これは、よくないメールだ。[linebreak]見たくない。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:I had a bad feeling. Whatever was in that email, it wasn't good. I didn't want to see it.[%p]"

msgid "14700:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕を、見るな……」[%p]"
msgstr "14700:[name]拓巳[line]D-Don't look at me.[%p]"

msgid "14800:視線を感じる。[linebreak]誰かに見られている。[linebreak]いつもよりも確かな感覚がある。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:I felt the gaze. Somebody was watching me. It felt stronger than it usually did.[%p]"

msgid "14900:周囲を見回す。[linebreak]この部屋には、僕と梨深以外には、誰もいない。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:I looked around. Nobody was here but me and Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "15000:僕の手が止まったので、梨深はやむなくそばを相手に悪戦苦闘中。[linebreak]僕の方は見ていない。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:I'd stopped feeding her, so Rimi had gone back to doing battle with her noodle bowl. She wasn't looking at me.[%p]"

msgid "15100:となれば、見ているのは、あいつしかいない。[linebreak]“その目だれの目？”って、問いかけるまでもない。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:Which meant there was only one person who could be looking at me. “Whose eyes are those?” I didn't even need to ask.[%p]"

msgid "15200:僕はうめきつつ、ＰＣの前へ。[linebreak]新着メールをチェックする。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I let out a moan as I headed to the PC. I checked my messages.[%p]"

msgid "15300:１通だけ、来ていた。[linebreak]送信者は――[%p]"
msgstr "15300:There was only one new message. Its sender was...[%p]"

msgid "15400:『将軍』[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "15500:[name]拓巳[line]「うぅ、くそぅ……くそぅ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "15500:[name]拓巳[line]Aah... Damn it! Damn it! Damn it![%p]"

msgid "15600:今度は、なにをするつもりだ？[linebreak]今度こそ、フェイクじゃなくて、ホントに七海を誘拐するつもり？[linebreak]それとも、いよいよ、僕を直接殺しに来るの？[%p]"
msgstr "15600:What did he want now? Was he going to kidnap Nanami for real this time? Or was he coming to kill me himself?[%p]"

msgid "15700:恐怖に全身の毛が逆立つ。[linebreak]うなじのチリチリとした感覚が、さらに強くなる。気持ち悪い。頭も少し痛い。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:The hairs on my body stood up in terror. The prickling at the back of my neck got even stronger. I felt sick. My head hurt a little, too.[%p]"

msgid "15800:僕を見ないでよ……！[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Please... Don't look at me.[%p]"

msgid "15900:震える指でマウスを操作し、メールを開いた。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I opened the email with shaking fingers on the mouse.[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、れ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "16100:なにも、書いてなかった。[linebreak]タイトルに『目覚めて』とあるだけ。[linebreak]本文は、真っ白だ。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:There was nothing there. The title just read, “Wake up.” There was no other text.[%p]"

msgid "16200:目覚めて……って、どういう意味だ？[linebreak]ギガロマニアックスとして目覚めろとか？\u3000まさかね……。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:Wake up? What was that supposed to mean? Awaken to my Gigalomaniac powers or something? No way.[%p]"

msgid "16300:初めて会ったときも、『将軍』は似たようなことを言っていた気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:It felt like Shogun had said something similar the first time we'd met.[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]拓巳[line]「バ、バカに、して……！」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]拓巳[line]S-Stop messing with me![%p]"

msgid "16500:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、ぼぼ、僕を、怯えさせて、そ、そんなに、楽しいかっ」[%p]"
msgstr "16500:[name]拓巳[line]I-I-Is it that fun to f-frighten me like this?[%p]"

msgid "16600:苛つく。と同時に、胸の奥にわだかまっている恐怖を振り払いたくて。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I started to get mad. And at the same time, I wanted to get rid of the fear that was building up deep in my chest.[%p]"

msgid "16700:キーボードに強く手の平を叩きつけた。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:I slammed my palm down against the keyboard.[%p]"

msgid "16800:スピーカーが、ノイズを発した。[linebreak]なにか変な操作でもしちゃったかな……？[%p]"
msgstr "16800:A noise came from the speakers. Had I broken something?[%p]"

msgid "16900:[name]将軍[line]「……ざめ……じか……」[%p]"
msgstr "16900:[name]将軍[line]... up...ti...[%p]"

msgid "17000:[name]拓巳[line]「……っ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "17000:[name]拓巳[line]...?![%p]"

msgid "17100:なにか、聞こえた……。[linebreak]ノイズに混じって、なにかが、聞こえたぞ……。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:I heard a sound. I heard something mixed in with the noise.[%p]"

msgid "17200:少し焦りながら、ＰＣを調べる。[linebreak]ＭＰ３プレイヤーは作動してない。[linebreak]ブラウザで動画サイトも開いてない。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:I checked the PC, a little worried. The MP3 Player wasn't running. I didn't have any video sites open in the browser, either.[%p]"

msgid "17300:『将軍』のメールにウイルスでも仕込んであったのかと思ったけど、ファイルらしきものはなにも添付されていない。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:I wondered if maybe Shogun had sent a virus along with the email, but there weren't any files attached to it.[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]将軍[line]「……ん……だ……」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]将軍[line]...n...t...[%p]"

msgid "17500:まただ、また聞こえた。[linebreak]息苦しい。額から汗がにじみ出てくる。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:Again. I was hearing it again. It hurt to breathe. Sweat was beading on my forehead.[%p]"

msgid "17600:そ、そうだ、音声を切れ。[linebreak]ＰＣの音声を、ミュートにしてやれば、こんな紛らわしいノイズ、すぐに聞こえなくなる。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:R-Right. I could just kill the sound. If I muted the computer's sound, the confusing noise would go away.[%p]"

msgid "17700:マウスで、画面右下のサウンド設定をクリック。[linebreak]表示されたボリュームコントロール設定画面の、全ミュートの項をチェック。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:I clicked on the sound icon in the bottom right of the screen. When the volume control menu popped up, I set everything to mute.[%p]"

msgid "17800:これで、なにも聞こえない。[linebreak]声と聞き間違えるような、そんなノイズも耳にしなくて済む。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:Now I wouldn't have to hear anything. That noise almost sounded like a voice, but whatever it was, I wouldn't have to hear it anymore.[%p]"

msgid "17900:僕は、疲れてるんだ。動揺してるんだ。そりゃ動揺もするよ。つい数時間前に、知り合いが２人、目の前で死んだんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:I was tired, confused, and on edge. Of course I was. I'd seen two people I know die right in front of me just a few hours before.[%p]"

msgid "18000:あやせのお見舞いに行った病院で、変なものも見たし。[linebreak]七海からも妙な電話があったし。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:And I'd seen something weird at the hospital when I'd went to see Ayase, too. Then there was that weird call from Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "18100:だから、さっきのノイズは、単なる聞き間違いだ――[%p]"
msgstr "18100:Whatever that noise was, it was just nerves.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]将軍[line]「……目覚めて」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]将軍[line]Wake up.[%p]"

msgid "18300:声が――[%p]"
msgstr "18300:A voice...[%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]将軍[line]「時間がないんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]将軍[line]There's no time.[%p]"

msgid "18500:スピーカーから――[%p]"
msgstr "18500:...from the speaker.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]将軍[line]「もうすぐ、サードメルトが起き――」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]将軍[line]The Third Melt is almost here.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]拓巳[line]Aah... Aah...[%p]"

msgid "18800:はっきりと、聞こえた。[linebreak]あいつだ……。『将軍』の声だ……。[linebreak]スクランブル交差点で僕に話しかけてきた声と、同じだ……！[%p]"
msgstr "18800:I heard it clearly. It was him… Shogun's voice! Just like when he'd spoken to me at Scramble Crossing![%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]拓巳[line]「な、な、なんでだよ！？\u3000ミュートに、し、したはずだろ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]拓巳[line]H-How?! I muted it![%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]梨深[line]「タク、さーどめるとって、なぁに？」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]梨深[line]Taku, what's the Third Melt?[%p]"

msgid "19100:梨深は相変わらず無垢な表情で、首を傾げている。[linebreak]僕はその梨深に詰め寄った。[linebreak]両肩をつかんで、揺さぶる。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:Rimi looked confused. The expression on her face was still one of childlike innocence. I rushed over to Rimi. I grabbed her by both shoulders and shook.[%p]"

msgid "19200:[name]拓巳[line]「り、梨深、頼むよ……しっかりしてよ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "19200:[name]拓巳[line]R-Rimi, please! Wake up![%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]梨深[line]「いた、いたいよぅ……」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]梨深[line]Ow! Y-You're hurting me![%p]"

msgid "19400:[name]拓巳[line]「言ってくれ、ぼ、僕を守るって、言ってくれよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "19400:[name]拓巳[line]S-Say it! Tell me you'll protect me![%p]"

msgid "19500:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕は、ひ、１人じゃ、耐えられない……このままじゃ、こ、殺される……！」[%p]"
msgstr "19500:[name]拓巳[line]I-I can't handle this alone. H-He's going to kill me![%p]"

msgid "19600:[name]梨深[line]「あうぅ、いたく、しないで……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "19600:[name]梨深[line]Aah! Please... don't hurt me.[%p]"

msgid "19700:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕は、き、君を、責めないから……！」[%p]"
msgstr "19700:[name]拓巳[line]I-I won't be mad at you![%p]"

msgid "19800:[name]拓巳[line]「き、君がいてくれないと、こ、困るんだ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "19800:[name]拓巳[line]I-I need you here for me![%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]拓巳[line]「だから……」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]拓巳[line]So...[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]梨深[line]「いたいの、やだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]梨深[line]Please don't hurt me.[%p]"

msgid "20100:梨深の瞳から、涙がこぼれた。[linebreak]僕は梨深を怯えさせている。[linebreak]彼女の肩が、小刻みに震えている。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:Tears fell from her eyes. I was scaring her. Her shoulders were shaking.[%p]"

msgid "20200:僕はゆっくりと手を離した。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:I slowly let go.[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]拓巳[line]「頼むよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]拓巳[line]Please...[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]拓巳[line]「目を、覚まし――」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]拓巳[line]Wake up—[%p]"

msgid "20500:[name]拓巳[line]「……え！？」[%p]"
msgstr "20500:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "20600:床が激しく揺れ始めた。[linebreak]地震……！？[linebreak]この前より大きい……！[%p]"
msgstr "20600:The floor began to shake violently. An earthquake? And it was bigger than the last one?[%p]"

msgid "20700:[name]拓巳[line]「……ぐぁぁぁっ」[%p]"
msgstr "20700:[name]拓巳[line]Gwaaah![%p]"

msgid "20800:激しい耳鳴り。[linebreak]頭が割れるほどの、甲高い共鳴音。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:There was a violent ringing in my ears, the high-pitched sound of something resonating in a way that threatened to split open my head.[%p]"

msgid "20900:耳に何千本もの細い針を突き刺されているようで。[linebreak]脳を、ミキサーでぐちゃぐちゃにかき回されているかのようで。[%p]"
msgstr "20900:It was like thousands of tiny needles being stabbed into my ears, and my brain being thrown into a blender.[%p]"

msgid "21000:そして――[%p]"
msgstr "21000:And then ...[%p]"

msgid "21100:すさまじい衝撃とともに、視界が白く染まった――[%p]"
msgstr "21100:With a terrible impact, my vision turned white.[%p]"

